      "title": "The value of the dollar increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Central Bank of Sri Lanka said that the selling price of the US dollar has slightly increased today.",
        "According to the report issued by the bank, the selling price of the US dollar has been recorded as 368.52 rupees.",
        "Meanwhile, the purchase value of the US dollar has also been recorded at 357.94 rupees. (R)"
      ],
